								</svg>
							</a>
						</li>
						<li id="linkedin" class="h-8 w-8 scaleImg">
							<a href="https://www.linkedin.com">
								<svg viewBox="0 0 72 72" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
									<path d="M8,72 L64,72 C68.418278,72 72,68.418278 72,64 L72,8 C72,3.581722 68.418278,-8.11624501e-16 64,0 L8,0 C3.581722,8.11624501e-16 -5.41083001e-16,3.581722 0,8 L0,64 C5.41083001e-16,68.418278 3.581722,72 8,72 Z" fill="#0B0D16"/>
