								</svg>
							</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<div id="description" class="flex flex-col">
						<span class="medium">Software engineer;</span>
						<span class="medium">Full stack developer.</span>						
					</div>
				</div>
				<div id="about" class="w-[60%] h-fit gap-4">
					<h2>About me</h2>
					<p class="mb-4">Developer with high attention to detail, mindful of time management, open-minded, team working, adaptable and excited to learn new things every day.</p>
