					<p class="mb-4">When leisuring you can find me painting miniatures, reading books, playing board games, video games or even in the gym.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="skills_career" class="flex flex-row w-full h-full pt-11 pb-48 px-8 gap-8">
				<div id="skills_tools" class="flex flex-col w-[40%] gap-11">
					<div id="skills" class="gap-4 h-fit w-fit">
						<h3>Skills</h3>
						<ul class="gap-6 grid grid-cols-3 pt-4">
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-20" data-after-content="HTML5">
								<Image src={html} class="object-contain" alt="HTML icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-20" data-after-content="CSS3">
								<Image src={css} class="object-contain" alt="CSS3 icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-20" data-after-content="Javascript">
								<Image src={js} class="object-contain" alt="Javascript icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-10" data-after-content="Python">
								<Image src={python} class="object-contain" alt="Python icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-10" data-after-content="Java">
								<Image src={java} class="object-contain" alt="Java icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-10" data-after-content="Bash">
								<Image src={bash} class="object-contain" alt="Bash icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble" data-after-content="C Sharp">
								<Image src={csharp} class="object-contain" alt="C Sharp icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble" data-after-content="C Plus Plus">
								<Image src={cpp} class="object-contain" alt="C Plus Plus icon"/>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div id="tools" class="gap-4 h-fit w-fit">
						<h3>Tools</h3>
						<ul class="gap-6 grid grid-cols-3 pt-4">
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-30" data-after-content="React">
								<Image src={react} class="object-contain" alt="React icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-30" data-after-content="Astro">
								<Image src={astro} class="object-contain" alt="Astro icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-30" data-after-content="Tanstack Query">
								<Image src={tanstackQuery} class="object-contain" alt="Tanstack Query icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-20" data-after-content="Tailwind CSS">
								<Image src={tailwind} class="object-contain" alt="Tailwind CSS icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-20" data-after-content="Docker">
								<Image src={docker} class="object-contain" alt="Docker icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-20" data-after-content="Spring Boot">
								<Image src={springboot} class="object-contain" alt="Spring Boot icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-10" data-after-content="Linux">
								<Image src={linux} class="object-contain" alt="Linux icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-10" data-after-content="Git">
								<Image src={git} class="object-contain" alt="Git icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble z-10" data-after-content="MkDocs">
								<Image src={mkdocs} class="object-contain" alt="MkDocs icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble" data-after-content="Figma">
								<Image src={figma} class="object-contain" alt="Figma icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble" data-after-content="Photoshop">
								<Image src={photoshop} class="object-contain" alt="Photoshop icon"/>
							</li>
							<li class="flex h-8 w-8 scaleImg speech-bubble" data-after-content="Jira">
								<Image src={jira} class="object-contain" alt="Jira icon"/>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div id="career" class="flex flex-col w-[60%] h-fit gap-3-">
					<h3>Career path</h3>
					<ol class="w-full h-fit flex flex-col pt-5">
						<li class="mb-8 p-3 w-full h-fit itemCareer">
							<div class="flex flex-row gap-2 w-full h-fit">
								<div class="w-[20%] p-2.5 h-fit items-center font-semibold">2021 — 2024</div>
								<div class="w-[80%] h-fit">
									<h5>Universidade de Aveiro</h5>
									<p>Bachelor's Degree in Informatics Engineering/Computer Science</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="mb-12 p-3 w-full h-fit itemCareer">
							<div class="flex flex-row gap-2 w-full h-fit">
								<div class="w-[20%] p-2.5 h-fit items-center font-semibold">2018 — 2019</div>
								<div class="w-[80%]">
									<h5>Instituto Emprego e Formação Profissional</h5>
									<p>Marketing Course and Internship</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="mb-12 w-full p-3 h-fit itemCareer">
							<div class="flex flex-row gap-2 w-full h-fit">
								<div class="w-[20%] p-2.5 h-fit items-center font-semibold">2016 — 2017</div>
								<div class="w-[80%]">
									<h5>Centroproduto</h5>
									<p>Video and Image Editing Specialist. Nine-month professional internship at a start-up.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="w-full p-3 h-fit itemCareer">
							<div class="flex flex-row gap-2 w-full h-fit">
								<div class="w-[20%] p-2.5 h-fit items-center font-semibold">2014 — 2016</div>
								<div class="w-[80%]">
									<h5>CESAE</h5>
									<p>Spent nearly three years completing my final educational qualifications.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ol>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		


		<div id="projects" class="flex flex-col w-full h-fit py-32 px-2.5 gap-6 items-center text-center">
			<h2 class="gap-2.5 py-6 w-full h-fit">Projects</h2>
			<div id="videogames_websites" class="flex flex-row w-full h-fit gap-2.5">
				<div id="video_games" class="p-2.5 gap-2.5 h-fit w-[49%]">
					<h3 class="pb-3">Video Games</h3>
					<ul class="w-full h-fit py-3.5 px-3 gap-2.5 text-left">
						<Content object={ticTacToe} last={false} isWebsite={false}/>
						<Content object={pong} last={false} isWebsite={false}/>
						<Content object={towerDefense} last={false} isWebsite={false}/>
						<Content object={projectBoost} last={true} isWebsite={false}/>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div id="videogames_websites_divider" class="border-1 border-solid border-[#A8B0C6] mt-4"/>
				<div id="websites" class="p-2.5 gap-2.5 h-fit w-[49%]">
					<h3 class="pb-3">Websites</h3>
					<ul class="w-full h-fit py-3.5 px-3 gap-2.5 text-left">
						<Content object={uaSmartSignage} last={false} isWebsite={true}/>
						<Content object={boardgamesHub} last={true} isWebsite={true}/>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	

		
		<div id="currentWork" class="flex flex-col w-full h-fit py-32 px-2.5 gap-3.5 items-center text-center">
			<h2 class="py-10 w-full">Currently working on</h2>
			<div class="flex flex-row w-full h-fit gap-3.5 px-10 pb-10">
				<div class="flex flex-col rounded-md outline-1 outline-[#A8B0C6] w-[50%] p-6">
					<h3>Dark Souls 2 Mod</h3><h5>Archipelago Randomizer</h5>
					<ul class="w-full h-fit py-10 px-10 space-y-2 gap-2.5 text-left">
						<li class="list-disc list-inside">Archipelago Randomizer mod for DS2;</li>
						<li class="list-disc list-inside">Randomize items based on location pickups;</li>
						<li class="list-disc list-inside">CheatEngine research for memory addresses;</li>
						<li class="list-disc list-inside">Reverse engineering with assembly;</li>
						<li class="list-disc list-inside">Creating client to connect with Archipelago.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col rounded-md outline-1 outline-[#A8B0C6] w-[50%] p-6">
					<h3>Entertainment Tracker</h3><h5>Sharing website</h5>
					<ul class="w-full h-fit py-10 px-10 space-y-2 gap-2.5 text-left">
						<li class="list-disc list-inside">Simple website to create various lists;</li>
						<li class="list-disc list-inside">Centralized place to have games, movies, etc;</li>
						<li class="list-disc list-inside">Cache information and use it for statistics.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>